                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable F</hi> 128.) I pursued the prisoner, and took him at the corner of Hart-street—I brought him to the prosecutor's shop, and took this handkerchief out of his pocket—she identified it directly—he said he was going by the house, was taken short, and went in to ease himself.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> In passing this house, I saw a man run by and drop this handkerchief; I took it up and ran after him.</p>
